  "description": "An externally attractive, practical and convenient in everyday use refrigerator from the advanced Serie 4 line from the popular Bosch brand. The model was introduced to the market in 2023 and is positioned by the manufacturer in the middle price range. The cooling and freezing chambers are equipped with the No Frost system, and the body itself corresponds to the Perfect Fit concept, thanks to which this model can be mounted with zero gaps between adjacent walls and furniture. If necessary, the unit can be built into a niche. The compressor system is represented by an inverter unit with digital electronic control. The Bosch KGN362WDF refrigerator has a total usable capacity of 321 liters. The refrigeration compartment with a volume of 218 liters boasts an increased VitaFresh freshness zone, there is also a separate section for storing meat and fish products at a temperature of 0 ° C. In turn, the freezing zone productivity reaches 10 kg/day, and the lowest temperature maintained inside reaches -24 °C. The freezer is well sealed and heat-insulated, and when the power supply is disconnected, the freezing temperature is maintained for 14 hours. The refrigerator uses a back wall with a special glossy High-Glossy Backwall. This is a decorative panel that helps to better distribute and retain cold.",
